# CQ-045: What memory blocks exist and what key-value pairs do they contain?
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX pao: <https://purl.org/pao/>
SELECT ?block ?key ?value WHERE {
  ?block a pao:MemoryBlock ;
         pao:hasBlockKey ?key ;
         pao:hasBlockValue ?value .
}
